quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  17,50,"Maakan …ìe -yo Nulaa…óo-:"Wonee -ko onon yo sirkoo…ìe-si tawii hi…óon hattani kaa∆¥e e sattugol mun,maa wonon njan…óe e doole mun,on hattantaake …óun"."
  17,51,"Maa…óun laatee tagu goo …ìurngu tii…óude e majji kannji …ói…ói, ko tawi no tii…ói ka …ìer…óe mon. Pellet, Alla ko O ruttoowo on wano O fuddori on non, O wurnitay on wano O tagiri on non ka laawol aranol, aray bee sanndal…óii…ìe ka wi'a: "Ko hommbo artirta men e ngurndan …ìaawo mayde amen?" Maakan …ìe: "Artiray on On Tagu…óo on ka laawol aranol ko aldaa e misal adiingal", aray ka …ìe dimmba ko'e ma…ì…ìe …óen hara ko …ìe jalnor…ìe ko jaabi…óaa …ìe kon, …ìe wi'a ko …ìe wo…ó…óintin…ìe: "Ko honnde tuma woni ngol ruttagol?!" Maakan …ìe: "no gasa …óun …ìadike, kala ko woni arude haray wo…ó…óaa."
  17,52,"Alla artiray on √±annde O noddata on faande ka leydi mofturu, nooto…óon ko on …óoftii…ìe yamiroore Makko nden, ko on yettu…ìe Mo, hara hi…óon sikka onon on √±ii…ìaano ka leydi si wanaa dummune hun fan…óukun."
  17,53,"Maakan -ko an yo Nulaa…óo- jeyaa…ìe an gom…óin…ìe …ìen: "yo …ìe wowlu konngol mo∆¥∆¥ol ngol tuma …ìe yewtata, …ìe wo…ó…óitoo konngol bonungol lancayngol ngol; sabu Seytaane huutoray ngol o golla hakkunde ma…ì…ìe huunde ko no bonnana …ìe ngurdan ma…ì…ìe aduna yankejan e laaharayankejan, pellet, Seytaane laatanike ne…ó…óanke ga√±o …ìanngu…óo ngayngu, no fawii ne…ó…óanke reenagol e Seytaane."
  17,54,"Joomi mon -ko onon yo yim…ìe- ko Anndu…óo fii mon, hay huunde suu…óanaaki Mo immorde e mon, si O yi…óii yurminnde on O yurminay on, …óun woni O hawrinndina on e gom…óinal e golle mo∆¥∆¥e. Si O yi…óii kadi nde O leptata on, O leptay on …óun woni O woppa on gaayi gom…óinal O wara on e hoore keefereeku, Men nulaali ma -ko an yo Nulaa…óo- e dow ma…ì…ìe fawtii…óo sakko doolaa…ìe e dow gom…óinal, ha…óaa …ìe e immorde e keeferaaku, moftanaa …ìe golleeji ma…ì…ìe …óin. Pellet, an ko a yottinanoowo Alla ko O yamirmaa yottinngol kon."
  17,55,"Ko Joomi maa…óa -an yo Nulaa…óo- woni Anndu…óo denndaangal …ìen wom…ìe ka kammuuli e ka leydi, ko O Anndu…óo alhaaliiji ma…ì…ìe e ko …ìe hanndi kon. Pellet, Men …ìurnii yoga e Annabaa…ìe …ìen e dow yoga sabu …óuu…óugol jokkoo…ìe …ìen e Tellinngol Defte, Men okki Daawuuda Deftere, nden le ko Jabuura."
  17,56,"Maakan -an yo Nulaa…óo- …ìee sirkoo…ìe: Noddee -Ko onon yo sirkoo…ìe- …ìen …ìe aa∆¥i…óon ko rewetee…ìe gaanin Alla si lorra jippike e mon, kam…ìe …ìe maraa feere duncugol lorra kan e mon, …ìe maraa kadi feere egginngol lorra kan faande e tanaa mon sabu ronkere ma…ì…ìe, on laatii…óo ko o ronku…óo o wonataa rewetee…óo."
  17,57,"∆Åen, …ìe noddoton immorde e Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen e ko nanndi e ma…ì…ìe, …ìen, kam…ìe tigi hi…ìe …óa…ìude ko …ìattina …ìe ka Alla immorde e golle mo∆¥∆¥e, hi…ìe foolondira ko hommbo e ma…ì…ìe …ìurata …ìattorde Mo …óoftaare, hi…ìe jortii kadi nde O Hinnotoo…ìe, hi…ìe huli kadi nde O leptata …ìe, pellet, lepte Joomi maa …óen -an yo Nulaa…óo- ko haanaa…óe huleede."
  17,58,"Alaa e ho…óo maa…óum saare si wanaa Menen Men jippinay e mayre lepte e halakuyee ka ngurndan aduna sabu yeddugol yim…ìe mayre, maa…óum Men jarribora nde lepte doolnu…óe, warngo maa tanaa …óun sabu yeddugol yim…ìe marye, ngol halkugol e warugol laatike √ëaawoore Alla winndaande ka Alluwal Reenaangal."